            <title>[CASSANDRA-6877] pig tests broken</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6877</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not sure what happened here, but I get a smorgasbord of errors running the pig tests now, from xml errors in xerces to NotFoundExceptions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
